Cagoul
======

Cagoul is a thin C++ wrapper of OpenGL, to provide additional typesafety and
facilitate RAII programming.

Copyright (C) 2010
John Bytheway <jbytheway at that gmail place>

Examples are the copyright of their respective authors, and may be subject to
different license conditions.

For building instructions see INSTALL.

For detailed documentation the docs can be built with 'make doc', and will
appear in the 'doc' directory.


